## VerusHash Porting Patch

This file contains human-maintained, unified-diff style notes for changes made while porting VerusHash into this xmrig-based miner.

- **Baseline**: upstream `Slashx124/xmrig-test` (`master`).
- **Note**: Only files that differ from the baseline and are relevant to VerusHash are recorded here.

Sections are grouped by file. Each section uses a diff-like style:

```diff
--- a/path/to/file.cpp   (upstream xmrig-test)
+++ b/path/to/file.cpp   (this ported tree)
@@ context
- old line(s)
+ new line(s)
```

